789cf69c-a121-4ce5-8dc2-05d58985bddd.title: Captain Tock
789cf69c-a121-4ce5-8dc2-05d58985bddd.text:
Ahoy, young lad. Might ye be able to help me, perhaps?
I be in a spot of bother.

options.text: What kind of help do you need?

a475eca5-c2a6-4eab-9736-0308d4fc93ea.title: <player>
a475eca5-c2a6-4eab-9736-0308d4fc93ea.text: What kind of help do you need?

f40a09a1-52d1-49e5-be73-a6d7b33746aa.title: Captain Tock
f40a09a1-52d1-49e5-be73-a6d7b33746aa.text:
It be about my crew. They be a lazy bunch at times,
but they be stout in the heart and strong in the arm,
and they don't deserve what's happened to them...

27cf2107-4c69-4d23-a88d-72a81bed9b71.title: Captain Tock
27cf2107-4c69-4d23-a88d-72a81bed9b71.text:
It be a curse! A curse has been laid upon my crew!
That's the only thing it can be.

f448c035-9f34-46d2-beae-6fd51fef737e.title: Captain Tock
f448c035-9f34-46d2-beae-6fd51fef737e.text:
So I need a young lad such as yerself to find a way to
lift the curse. Will ye help me?

89cf0bd1-9dea-46a2-b806-f03e410e3a44.title: Captain Tock
89cf0bd1-9dea-46a2-b806-f03e410e3a44.text:
I be the Corsair Captain!
Captain of the Corsairs of Corsair Cove!
My gallant band of corsairs are famed in song and
story among all seafarers.

options.text: That's very interesting; do tell me more.

9a3f3420-9d00-4f6f-8cd6-2104410c5491.title: Captain Tock
9a3f3420-9d00-4f6f-8cd6-2104410c5491.text:
Arrr... well, ye can boast of yer ignorance if ye likes,
but it don't make ye sound smarter.

a7370b42-c85c-401e-9b5c-9fb82cefa500.title: Captain Tock
a7370b42-c85c-401e-9b5c-9fb82cefa500.text:
Well, as I were saying, young lad, I be in a spot of
bother, and I thought ye might be able to help.

options.text: What kind of help do you need?

30f237e0-da85-4d37-a15e-ff60343fb52f.title: <player>
30f237e0-da85-4d37-a15e-ff60343fb52f.text: That's very interesting; do tell me more.
